dc_title_s: [Geological Survey of England and Wales : one inch to the mile map. New Series.] Bridlington, drift, sheet 65
dc_description_s: Geological Survey of Great Britain. Great Britain. Geological Survey of England and Wales. Sheet 65 drift. Great Britain. Geological Survey of England and Wales. North Decimal Degree 54.100000. South Decimal Degree 53.9333. East Decimal Degree 0.1667. West Decimal Degree -0.2667. In upper left margin: Ordnance Survey of England and Wales. In upper right margin: Old Series Sheet 94 N.E. Relief shown by contour interval and spot heights. Transverse Mercator projection. National grid system. "Geological information published Dec. 1882. Printed 1909.".
